    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《费格先生》是一款无情的俯视视角动作解谜游戏，你将扮演费格先生——一个因悲剧和实验而诞生的可爱类章鱼人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备只有炸药（或许还有几根触手），你需要穿越危险的地下城、虚幻的洞窟和炽热的熔岩坑。你的终极目标？摧毁创造你实验室的根基。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >穿越异次元空间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/84d37227649e6fb7b89a6867126ca15f.poster.avif?t=1766428437\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/84d37227649e6fb7b89a6867126ca15f.webm?t=1766428437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/84d37227649e6fb7b89a6867126ca15f.mp4?t=1766428437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >炸毁一切</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/14ce60e12ac54e6452ef41cf6c13217f.poster.avif?t=1766428437\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/14ce60e12ac54e6452ef41cf6c13217f.webm?t=1766428437\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/14ce60e12ac54e6452ef41cf6c13217f.mp4?t=1766428437\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽量别死</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/6dcb0874c1ea24cf71906a0dfdf9c24e.poster.avif?t=1766428437\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122220/extras/6dcb0874c1ea24cf71906a0dfdf9c2